name: Air Canada 777-333ER [C-FIUL] Sunset Landing in Calgary
description:
Well this was quite a sight! I'm glad I managed to catch this beauty, thanks to the help of CYUL Plane Spotter once again ;) YYC never sees 777s in the winter, except to clear backlogs of passengers if there's been a lot of cancellations. Anyway, I hope you guys enjoy this sunset footage :)

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
